<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Indicator Corridor - Quantitative</h3>

    <p>A metal corridor lined with glass orbs, each filled with glowing red-gold fluid. The walls are digital planes abundant with light, <a class="panelOpener" identifier="numbers">numbers flashing by too rapidly to read</a>. Set in the middle of the eastern wall is a <a class="whiteMarker glassScreen" board="22">glass screen.</a></p>

    <p>The corridor runs <a class="panelOpener" identifier="north">nor��4۩</a> and [[south|indicatorCorridorQualitative]]. Steps to the [[east|glassTowerStairwell]] down to an open glass door, beyond which you can see a stairwell. A bronze slab hangs on a heavy oaken door to the [[west|diningHall]].</p>
</div>

</snippet>


<snippet name="indicatorCorridorQualitative" tags="amberworks">

<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Indicator Corridor - Qualitative</h3>

    <p>A metal corridor lined with glass orbs, each crackling with energy. The walls are digital planes abundant with light, words in an unknown language scrolling past at breakneck pace.</p>

    <p>The corridor runs [[north|indicatorCorridorQuantitative]] and [[south|nexusDome]]. An elegant wooden door inlaid with glass and gold leads to the [[east|clockLounge]], with a thick <a class="whiteMarker glassScreen" board="23">glass screen</a> dangling from its handle. A nondescript wooden door leads to the [[west|redLounge1]].</p>
</div>

</snippet>

<snippet name="nexusDome" tags="amberworks">

<div class="menuPanel absoluteAlign hidden" identifier="machine">
