<div class="absoluteAlign topHalf">
</div>
<div class="absoluteAlign bottomHalf blackBg">
    <h3 class="roomName">Nexus Dome</h3>

    <p>A dizzying range of colors filters down from a stained-glass dome, under which rests a cage-like <a class="panelOpener" identifier="machine">apparatus</a> made of interlocking bronze arms. Gold pipes and wires extend out from the base of the cage, running under the glass-topped floor into the walls. Wires run from a <a class="whiteMarker glassScreen" board="24">glass screen</a> into the ceiling.</p>

    <p>From the corridor to the [[north|indicatorCorridorQualitative]], you see flashes of red light. A sliding glass door, behind which you can see smudges of red and white, leads [[east|sinkhouse]]. Steam hisses from a corridor to the [[south|gearCorridor]].</p>
</div>
</snippet>


<snippet name="gearCorridor" tags="amberworks">

<div class="menuPanel absoluteAlign hidden" identifier="south">
